@@ -77,0 +77,14 @@
+ifeq ($(call isTargetOs, macosx)+$(call isTargetCpu, aarch64)+$(INCLUDE_COMPILER2), true+true+true)

+      CFLAGS := $(NEON_CFLAGS), \

+  TARGETS += $(BUILD_LIBSLEEF)
+endif
